headline: Voda Cleaning & Restoration Appoints Sae Lee as Chief Financial Officer and Chief Strategy Officer
summary: Voda Cleaning & Restoration, one of the fastest-growing cleaning & restoration franchise brands in the U.S., announced today the appointment of Sae Lee as its new Chief Financial Officer (CFO) and Chief Strategy Officer (CSO). The executive hire marks a pivotal step for Voda (and its parent company Franchise Playbook) as it nears its 100th franchise owner milestone in just over two years of franchising and enters a new era of expansion and operational scale.
